import React, { Component } from 'react'
import Fullpage, { FullPageSections, FullpageSection } from '@ap.cx/react-fullpage'
import '../App.css';

export default class App extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Fullpage>

            <FullPageSections>

                <FullpageSection className="s1"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s2"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s3"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s4"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s5"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s6"></FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s7">1</FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s8">2</FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s9">3</FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s10">1</FullpageSection>
                <FullpageSection className="s11">2</FullpageSection>
                

            </FullPageSections>

        </Fullpage>
        )
    }
}
